    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/chapter-1/article-i/section-sec.-1.11"
             temporalId="sSEC_ 1_11">
      <num>SEC. 1.11</num>
      <heading>Same—Imprisonment of violators</heading>
      <content>
        <p>Any person sentenced to imprisonment for the violation of any provision of this code
               or of any ordinance of this city may be imprisoned.</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 24.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
